		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Green paper clips was entirely my idea, I take full responsibility for that.  I just wanted something that would <span style="color: #00FF00">immediately stand out and attract attention</span>.  Obviously, the old icon made for a white background wouldn't work, and a dark icon wouldn't work against the dark blue-gray background.  I also tried adding a white outline to a black paper clip, and that looked horrible.<br />It kinda matches the logo at the top, even though it is a different shade of green.<br />The paper clip is the exact same shape as the standard icon, just with an added black outline, and it's now bright green.<br /><br />If you're really prefer CGA/EGA color #7, I could make it that color as well.

		

